  <section class="pg-hero">
    <h1>How Much Melatonin Is Safe? Maximum Dosage & Side Effects</h1>
    <p class="pg-sub">Americans pop melatonin gummies like candy — but a JAMA study found 88% of products contain more melatonin than labeled. This evidence-based guide covers the real safety limits, what happens when you take too much, drug interactions to watch for, and who should avoid melatonin entirely.</p>
    <div class="pg-meta">
      <span>Updated March 2026</span>
      <span>22 Studies Reviewed</span>
      <span>Registered Dietitian Authored</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Breadcrumbs items={[
    { label: 'Blog', href: '/blog/' },
    { label: 'How Much Melatonin Is Safe?', href: '/blog/how-much-melatonin-is-safe/' },
  ]} />

  <div class="w">

    <AuthorBox
      publishDate="2026-03-29"
      updateDate="2026-03-29"
      authorName="Sarah Mitchell"
